name: genpy
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "genpy" %}
{% set version = "2016.1.3" %}
{% set sha256 = "1c11726f1e8ace8bbdfc87816403c9a59f53a8c3d45c99187ae17c9725d87a91" %}

package:
    name: {{ name|lower }}
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
    number: 0
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
        - six
        - numpy
        - pytools
    run:
        - python
        - numpy
        - pytools
        - six

test:
    imports:
        - {{ name }}

about:
    home: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/{{ name }}
    license: MIT
    license_file: LICENSE
    summary: AST-based Python source generation
    dev_url: http://github.com/inducer/{{ name }}

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - inducer
